episodes.title: Part I: Piercing "The Vow" w/ Mark Vicente
episodes.description: Part 1 of our 2-part interview with Mark VicenteMark Vicente - Author, speaker, and award-winning Writer/Director/Producer Mark Vicente was part of the creative team behind the sleeper hit “What The Bleep Do We Know?!” He and his wife’s harrowing campaign to escape and expose the organization NXIVM, a coercive and duplicitous high-control group, is captured in both seasons of the critically acclaimed  HBO Documentary Series “THE VOW”.Instagram: @markvicente Linktree: https://linktr.ee/markvicente Stay tuned for news about Mark’s upcoming film at https://www.instagram.com/empathynotincluded/Podcast WTF is on my Mind?!https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/wtf-is-on-my-mind/id1646783869https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCX1OsELrINqvPVImbyM6qdQMark’s website: www.markvicente.comSupport Mark’s work: https://www.patreon.com/MarkVicenteBook a 1 on 1 with Terra for trauma/ toxic relationship coaching https://calendly.com/terranewell91/15-minute-coaching-consult?month=2023-06
